data.description: Welcome to the perfect starter home nestled in the Settlers Way subdivision within the thriving city of Anna. Inside, you'll immediately notice the spacious & welcoming open concept floor plan that seamlessly connects the kitchen & living room. The oversized bedrooms provide ample space for relaxation or a versatile space for a home office. The expansive backyard backs up to a heavily treed greenbelt & encourages outdoor activities, gardening, and endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment. Additionally, the location of this home offers quick and convenient access to shopping, restaurants, and schools. This property is the perfect place to begin your homeownership journey. With its open concept design, spacious bedrooms, and a backyard backing up to a lush greenbelt, it truly offers a well-rounded and comfortable living experience.
